        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Conductor', 3: 'In the recurrence just now, I observed some very unusual emotional fluctuations in all of you—especially the two of you, Bianca and Karenina. Your emotional fluctuations were more violent than those of others.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 19,
        "ActionId": 19,
